Information reimagined

Opportunity to Sponsor OpenText World 2025

 
Dear Partner,

Preparations for OpenText World 2025 are full steam ahead, and there’s still time to get involved as a sponsor! We’re thrilled to be bringing the event to life from November 17–20 at the Music City Center in Nashville—and we’d love for you to be part of it.

Following the success of our events this year, we’ve taken Partner feedback to heart and completely reimagined our sponsorship program to deliver more visibility, deeper engagement, and greater impact.
2025 Sponsorship Prospectus
What’s New for 2025?
The updated sponsorship offerings are designed to help you stand out, connect with the right audience, and achieve your business goals:
  • A fresh, exciting location! The venue combines modern elegance with Nashville’s rich cultural spirit — all set against the dynamic backdrop of downtown energy.
  • Innovative booth designs that maximize visibility and foot traffic
  • Expanded speaker packages to highlight your thought leadership on larger stages
  • Broader branding opportunities across digital, onsite, and experiential channels
  • Flexible engagement models aligned to your specific business objectives

Whether you're looking to grow brand awareness, build pipeline, or deepen relationships, OpenText World 2025 offers the platform to do it all.
2025 Sponsorship Prospectus
Why Sponsor?
OpenText World brings together thousands of global decision-makers, IT leaders, developers, and innovators to explore how AI and information management are transforming the way we work and grow. Sponsorship gives your brand a powerful presence in this high-impact environment.

Want to know more?
We’re pleased to introduce Nathalie Pelé, as your dedicated contact for OpenText World 2025 sponsorships. She’s here to support your planning and help tailor the right package for your goals.

Reach out to Nathalie at sponsorships@opentext.com for questions, pricing, availability, or next steps.

We hope to see you at the heart of OpenText World 2025—connecting with customers, showcasing innovation, and creating lasting impact.

Let’s build something amazing together.

Warm regards,
The OpenText Events Team
